item.title: These Are the Most Motivational Books Ever Written
item.description:
These Are the Most Motivational Books Ever Written

Three years ago, I identified the "Top 10 Motivational Books of All Time," but with a twist: I left the #1 spot blank and asked Inc.com readers to name their favorite. In hundreds of comments, our readers named almost 300 books but there were 18 that turned up consistently.
